    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Ws18DrzbCb4p"
      },
      "source": [
        "## 4. PBR Parameter Configuration\n",
        "\n",
        "Define all 16 PBR output parameters. Each parameter is either a **texture map** (output via a decoder as an image) or a **scalar** value.\n",
        "\n",
        "| Parameter | Type | Channels | Latent Dim |\n",
        "|---|---|---|---|\n",
        "| Base Color / Albedo | RGB texture | 3 | 256 |\n",
        "| Metallic | Grayscale texture | 1 | 256 |\n",
        "| Roughness | Grayscale texture | 1 | 256 |\n",
        "| Specular | RGB texture | 3 | 256 |\n",
        "| Glossiness | Grayscale texture | 1 | 256 |\n",
        "| Normal Map | XYZ texture | 3 | 256 |\n",
        "| Ambient Occlusion | Grayscale texture | 1 | 256 |\n",
        "| Height / Displacement | Grayscale texture | 1 | 256 |\n",
        "| Opacity / Alpha | Grayscale texture | 1 | 256 |\n",
        "| Emissive | RGB texture | 3 | 256 |\n",
        "| Subsurface Scattering | RGB texture | 3 | 256 |\n",
        "| Transmission | Scalar | 1 | — |\n",
        "| IOR | Scalar | 1 | — |\n",
        "| Anisotropy | Scalar | 1 | — |\n",
        "| Anisotropic Rotation | Scalar | 1 | — |\n",
        "| Specular Tint | Scalar | 1 | — |"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 49,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Enabled PBR parameters: ['base_color', 'metallic', 'roughness', 'specular', 'normal_map', 'ao', 'height']\n",
            "  Texture maps: ['base_color', 'metallic', 'roughness', 'specular', 'normal_map', 'ao', 'height']\n",
            "  Scalars: []\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "# PBR Parameter Registry\n",
        "# Each entry: (name, type, output_channels, latent_dim, enabled_by_default)\n",
        "PBR_PARAMS = [\n",
        "    # Texture map outputs (decoded from latent vectors)\n",
        "    (\"base_color\",    \"rgb_texture\",   3, 256, True),\n",
        "    (\"metallic\",      \"gray_texture\",  1, 256, True),\n",
        "    (\"roughness\",     \"gray_texture\",  1, 256, True),\n",
        "    (\"specular\",      \"rgb_texture\",   3, 256, True),\n",
        "    (\"glossiness\",    \"gray_texture\",  1, 256, False),  # inverse of roughness\n",
        "    (\"normal_map\",    \"xyz_texture\",   3, 256, True),\n",
        "    (\"ao\",            \"gray_texture\",  1, 256, True),\n",
        "    (\"height\",        \"gray_texture\",  1, 256, True),\n",
        "    (\"opacity\",       \"gray_texture\",  1, 256, False),\n",
        "    (\"emissive\",      \"rgb_texture\",   3, 256, False),\n",
        "    (\"sss\",           \"rgb_texture\",   3, 256, False),\n",
        "    # Scalar outputs\n",
        "    (\"transmission\",  \"scalar\",        1, 1,   False),\n",
        "    (\"ior\",           \"scalar\",        1, 1,   False),\n",
        "    (\"anisotropy\",    \"scalar\",        1, 1,   False),\n",
        "    (\"aniso_rotation\",\"scalar\",        1, 1,   False),\n",
        "    (\"specular_tint\", \"scalar\",        1, 1,   False),\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Build config dict for easy access\n",
        "pbr_config = {}\n",
        "for name, ptype, channels, latent, enabled in PBR_PARAMS:\n",
        "    pbr_config[name] = {\n",
        "        \"type\": ptype,\n",
        "        \"channels\": channels,\n",
        "        \"latent_dim\": latent,\n",
        "        \"enabled\": enabled,\n",
        "    }\n",
        "\n",
        "# Enable/disable parameters here\n",
        "def get_enabled_params():\n",
        "    return {k: v for k, v in pbr_config.items() if v[\"enabled\"]}\n",
        "\n",
        "def get_texture_params():\n",
        "    return {k: v for k, v in get_enabled_params().items() if v[\"type\"] != \"scalar\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "def get_scalar_params():\n",
        "    return {k: v for k, v in get_enabled_params().items() if v[\"type\"] == \"scalar\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "enabled = get_enabled_params()\n",
        "print(f\"Enabled PBR parameters: {list(enabled.keys())}\")\n",
        "print(f\"  Texture maps: {list(get_texture_params().keys())}\")\n",
        "print(f\"  Scalars: {list(get_scalar_params().keys())}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 4b. Network Architecture Configuration\n",
        "\n",
        "Use the interactive GUI below to configure the encoder hidden layers, ResBlock toggles, and latent dimension. Click **\"Apply to Model\"** to write the config directly into `NETWORK_CONFIG`. Then re-run the **Model Definition** cell and **Training Setup** cell to rebuild the model with your new architecture."
      ]
    },
